{"tid":1427633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位文宣巴打，我有一個大膽既想法","createTime":"2019-08-07T07:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T07:18:14.000Z","uid":185730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"03787d23925fe3c409f4005dc44d6966d5036461","tid":1427633,"uid":185730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:05:14.000Z","msg":"既然班藍屍成日強調經濟穩定<br />\n點解文宣唔考慮一下利用班黑社會做文章<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如話721全港所有行業大停頓<br />\n86北角全部商店提早休息<br />\n<br />\n我地將全部責任推比黑社會同警犬<br />\n話佢地口說愛國但真正鼓吹罷工就係佢地。<br />\n甚至為左達成目的故意進行恐怖襲擊<br />\n民居開槍<br />\n佢地先係想玉石俱焚既一方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1827e02a460b41bfc00b9ad8ae0be0a50c3c17e","tid":1427633,"uid":185730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997c21ef44a7bdeb5e532affb19d6ab831814ca1","tid":1427633,"uid":185730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539cc745340bc059f631ffaad36ba0e3dfdb5e1e","tid":1427633,"uid":185730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793485f91856fb22606e56d921eaafb767473f88","tid":1427633,"uid":185730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:18:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}